      <h3>Why Virtual Reality</h3>
      <p>One of the best ways to fall in love with a wine is to walk through the vineyards and wineries from which it is produced while soaking up the sights, sounds, and smells associated with the process of creating the wine. </p>
      <p>Although there are no smells or tactile sensations involved in virtual reality (yet), my guess was that being immersed in a virtual vineyard could be an engaging and educational experience.</p>
